wingedwarrior41@... writes:


&gt; Belthassan looked at the cat, almost showing empathy.
&gt; 
&gt; Belthassan: First, I must tell you that restoring your old form can&#39;t
&gt; be done and would be utterly useless. That technology has been
&gt; obsolete for a long time and can&#39;t be replicated. Also, your actual
&gt; mode seems much more performing than your previous one, whatever it
&gt; was. Now as for who we Tripredacus are...

&quot;Hardly,&quot; she growled. In my form I was much larger. In this one I don&#39;t weld 
plasma cannons, nor laser cannons, or the incredible exostructure. & how am I 
to function in this fleeting form? Hmm? I suppose that energon is drained 
once more?&quot;

&gt; 
&gt; He went over to an old pipe and sat there.
&gt; 
&gt; Belthassan: We are descendants from a great Transformer who diverged
&gt; from the Autobot ranks and went underground. No archives have been
&gt; preserved of him. He established his faction and the millenias made us
&gt; evolve to what we are today. Right now, we are busy pacifying
&gt; Cybertron from our recent conquest of it. We drove off the main forces
&gt; of Maximals and the few Predacons who did not cooperate. They are
&gt; respectively the descendants of the Autobots and Decepticons. In other
&gt; words... (he glared at her) we are the masters of Cybertron!

&quot;No records of this Transformer, eh? I believe that there may still be.&quot; She 
paced a moment, then stopped & rested her clawed paw/hands upon her hips. 
&quot;The only Master of Cybertron, is Megatron! Conquerer of all of Cybertron.&quot;

She turned around. &quot;As to my older form being fleeting, we shall see about 
that. You forget, if this is of a different age, my own knowledge is of a 
different age as well.&quot; shifting to a more deadly tone. &quot;I know not who you 
are, or of the others you speak of, but I am a Decepticon. My loyality is to 
Megatron & his wishes.&quot;

&quot;Now... must I tear apart this world in search of what I need alone? Or will 
I gain cooperation? It&#39;s not good to be against me, rest assured you say the 
same that I should not betray you. But.. how many Transformers do you know 
who have survived since the time of the Great War? Hmm?&quot; Her optics were icy 
but a slight old glint was in them. She had many ideas. In her &#39;mind&#39; she 
still had skematics of her old form. The form that was an upgrade by 
Scrapper. She enjoyed this one the best. 


